Focuses on 2D skeletal animations, allowing more fluid movements than frame-based animations.
Integrates with Unity, Unreal, and many other engines through runtime libraries.
Reduces file sizes compared to frame-based animations by reusing skeletal assets.
Allows for skin swapping and animation blending to create varied character animations.
Offers powerful IK (inverse kinematics) and mesh deformation tools.
A paid tool with a free trial available for evaluation.

Website: http://esotericsoftware.com
